        "content": "# üåü Message & Schema Handling Workflow  \n\n## üöÄ Overview  \nThe AI Agent processes database schema **from a local file**, transforming it into a **JSON object** for improved efficiency.  \n\n## üîπ Key Benefits  \n- **‚ö° Faster Processing**: Avoids slow remote database queries for schema retrieval.  \n- **üîç Schema Awareness**: The Agent understands the database structure **without accessing actual data**.  \n\n## üîÑ Workflow Steps  \n1. **Extract schema from a local file** ‚Üí Convert it into **JSON**.  \n2. **Convert DB schema into a long string**.  \n3. **Merge** schema with **Chat Trigger JSON fields** before sending input to the Agent node.  ",
